lockquote><blockquote>Kotlin <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實而家已經有一大堆JVM languages, 大家得閒可以玩下:<br />\nClojure<br />\nFrege<br />\nGroovy<br />\nJRuby<br />\nJython<br />\nKotlin<br />\nScala<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但寫android既話應該都係用番java/kotlin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nserver/其他野就另計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee5a2a0eb28b425240e4cfaae39318c57fb530b","tid":248751,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T11:53:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Kotlin <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實而家已經有一大堆JVM languages, 大家得閒可以玩下:<br />\nClojure<br />\nFrege<br />\nGroovy<br />\nJRuby<br />\nJython<br />\nKotlin<br />\nScala<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但寫android既話應該都係用番java/kotlin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nserver/其他野就另計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc47cbc7ea94e004eda51e4fe621949af7c2349","tid":248751,"uid":26235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T11:54:34.000Z","msg":"而家塵世間多唔多公司請js人 會唔會用node 做back end"},{"pid":"63106874db371695bad9fdc07e4594585ad6b372","tid":248751,"uid":6801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T11:56:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家塵世間多唔多公司請js人 會唔會用node 做back end</blockquote><br />\n大把"},{"pid":"b9e19a84253266a2a4ac9ca0562818163b07c4e3","tid":248751,"uid":6801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T11:57:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Kotlin <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實而家已經有一大堆JVM languages, 大家得閒可以玩下:<br />\nClojure<br />\nFrege<br />\nGroovy<br />\nJRuby<br />\nJython<br />\nKotlin<br />\nScala<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但寫android既話應該都係用番java/kotlin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nserver/其他野就另計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家google仲要正式俾番個名份kotlin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nJ死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67bd3738a28833fe6d3e7da0b76ac5857c2a1a39","tid":248751,"uid":68589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T12:48:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家塵世間多唔多公司請js人 會唔會用node 做back end</blockquote><br />\n大把</blockquote><br />\n呢條問題由三四年前問到宜家<br />\nnodejs已經過左最興旺既時期<br />\n宜家開始係興serverless<br />\nnodejs做到既web app endpoint, aws, google都已經做到<br />\nstartup要你識nodejs之餘一定要識埋呢堆"},{"pid":"a6e77e95c95e8e28bab563039d304a478ef8aabf","tid":248751,"uid":23699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:06:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Kotlin <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實而家已經有一大堆JVM languages, 大家得閒可以玩下:<br />\nClojure<br />\nFrege<br />\nGroovy<br />\nJRuby<br />\nJython<br />\nKotlin<br />\nScala<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n望左望kotlin 覺得好過Scala"},{"pid":"f5738cc84b77e660d557990fd0ec366618b8d50e","tid":248751,"uid":6801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:09:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Kotlin <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實而家已經有一大堆JVM languages, 大家得閒可以玩下:<br />\nClojure<br />\nFrege<br />\nGroovy<br />\nJRuby<br />\nJython<br />\nKotlin<br />\nScala<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n望左望kotlin 覺得好過Scala</blockquote><br />\n但scala個pattern matching好似勁過kotlin做到既野"},{"pid":"2279bbfe54d595dd474ad9eaaea359f79854c99b","tid":248751,"uid":23699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:41:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Kotlin <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實而家已經有一大堆JVM languages, 大家得閒可以玩下:<br />\nClojure<br />\nFrege<br />\nGroovy<br />\nJRuby<br />\nJython<br />\nKotlin<br />\nScala<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n望左望kotlin 覺得好過Scala</blockquote><br />\n但scala個pattern matching好似勁過kotlin做到既野</blockquote><br />\n我覺得kotlin係現代版 lightweight java<br />\n容易啲俾人migrate <br />\n<br />\nScala 好複雜 好多好神奇既feature<br />\n但啲docs真心差 <br />\n啲library 又勁用啲神奇feature<br />\n而且隔一兩個version 個份doc 巳經唔同哂<br />\n有時唔睇source 都唔知佢想點<br />\n佢個compiler 更加慢到嘔電 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb66071456acca66364fd0e68db0bb4ec8d33ea","tid":248751,"uid":56487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:50:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家塵世間多唔多公司請js人 會唔會用node 做back end</blockquote><br />\n大把</blockquote><br />\n呢條問題由三四年前問到宜家<br />\nnodejs已經過左最興旺既時期<br />\n宜家開始係興serverless<br />\nnodejs做到既web app endpoint, aws, google都已經做到<br />\nstartup要你識nodejs之餘一定要識埋呢堆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港難請人<br />\n寫server 我請php/java 唔好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋nodejs 你要寫到production grade 都唔係容易<br />\n都係拎黎整poc/ service 仔最好"},{"pid":"dd6232eaae032a9b062227c2e04237a5f1220936","tid":248751,"uid":26235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:20:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家塵世間多唔多公司請js人 會唔會用node 做back end</blockquote><br />\n大把</blockquote><br />\n呢條問題由三四年前問到宜家<br />\nnodejs已經過左最興旺既時期<br />\n宜家開始係興serverless<br />\nnodejs做到既web app endpoint, aws, google都已經做到<br />\nstartup要你識nodejs之餘一定要識埋呢堆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港難請人<br />\n寫server 我請php/java 唔好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋nodejs 你要寫到production grade 都唔係容易<br />\n都係拎黎整poc/ service 仔最好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都見而家大部分公司都仲係java back end<br />\n我只係用過angular 2寫front end 上prod<br />\n好好奇node 點做到java個類型既architecture"},{"pid":"32386370326b2a455a4f9946f56603f2080b3e98","tid":248751,"uid":6801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:54:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Kotlin <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實而家已經有一大堆JVM languages, 大家得閒可以玩下:<br />\nClojure<br />\nFrege<br />\nGroovy<br />\nJRuby<br />\nJython<br />\nKotlin<br />\nScala<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n望左望kotlin 覺得好過Scala</blockquote><br />\n但scala個pattern matching好似勁過kotlin做到既野</blockquote><br />\n我覺得kotlin係現代版 lightweight java<br />\n容易啲俾人migrate <br />\n<br />\nScala 好複雜 好多好神奇既feature<br />\n但啲docs真心差 <br />\n啲library 又勁用啲神奇feature<br />\n而且隔一兩個version 個份doc 巳經唔同哂<br />\n有時唔睇source 都唔知佢想點<br />\n佢個compiler 更加慢到嘔電 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nscala compiler慢呢樣真係死穴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60d9504bca7a455bc9f4da33d9dca009ade4a0a","tid":248751,"uid":75692,"